{"tid":1325182,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"反送中下 ，原唱羅文","createTime":"2019-07-16T19:43:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T19:55:00.000Z","uid":36833,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"72eff5f8d11b24547fd54fe034028c40304fb50f","tid":1325182,"uid":36833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T19:43:23.000Z","msg":"民主中有歡喜 抗爭亦常有淚<br />\n我哋大家 在反送中下相遇上<br />\n總算是團結多於唏噓<br />\n<br />\n抗爭不免崎嶇 難以絕無掛慮<br />\n既是同舟 在反送中下且共濟<br />\n拋棄區分求共對<br />\n<br />\n放開理非勇武矛盾 普選一起去追<br />\n同舟人 誓相隨 無畏更無懼<br />\n<br />\n同處暴政之邊 攜手踏平崎嶇<br />\n我哋大家 用艱辛努力寫下那<br />\n不朽香江名句<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n訓唔著改下，發覺好多詞都岩用"},{"pid":"db9b86a713fad26d5307c95f3a4bfc3f568e0b17","tid":1325182,"uid":36833,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T19:45:06.000Z","msg":"笑鬼死 ，係咪有負評機械人俾負評架"},{"pid":"4ef7f04145822f549b865ea6bf32d9d78ed51941","tid":1325182,"uid":182096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T19:53:11.000Z","msg":"詞確實對 <br />\n但音唔對 似教會歌"},{"pid":"15c00d7dd1e88cb7cc4f923fc0f001d39d255d5c","tid":1325182,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T19:55:00.000Z","msg":"教會ching?<br />\n改個首to the lord 好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}